default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultNovo Nordisk is a global healthcare company with 90 years of innovation and leadership in diabetes care.
default 
defaultThe company also has leading positions within haemophilia care, growth hormone therapy and hormone replacement therapy. Headquartered in Denmark, Novo Nordisk employs about 32,500 people in 74 countries and markets its products in 179 countries.
